Package: floritaly
Type: Package
Title: Access the Checklist of Italian Vascular Flora
Version: 1.11.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Gianni", "Bedini", , "gianni.bedini@unipi.it", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
    person("Matteo", "Conti", , "matteo.conti@phd.units.it", role = c("aut", "cre","cph"))
Description: Access the "Checklist of Italian vascular flora", bundled as
    three dataframes named all names (accepted and synonyms), accepted names with associated data, 
    and parsed names. In addition, it offers the namestand() function 
    to standardise a set of names against the Checklist, and the ckl_datalink()
    function to link scientific names to the regional distribution data included in 
    the Checklist.
